      "solution": "k = gets.to_i\ns = gets.chomp\n\nputs s.chars.map { |c|\n  v = c.ord\n  (v % 2 == 0 ? v + k : v - k).chr\n}.join",
      "statement": "Encrypt a given message based on the parity of each character's ASCII value.\nFor every character in the string S:\n\nIf its ASCII value is even, add K to it.\n\nIf its ASCII value is odd, subtract K from it.",
